{
  "description": "Generic lexicons for extracting the customer's REQUESTED workshop / working-session structure — candidate scenarios (with the data sources named inside each), the data sources to include, required participants, data constraints, timing, and whether procurement is needed yet. Linguistic shapes/theme terms only — never a company, product, speaker, or specific transcript. Logic lives in src/lib/decision-packet/workshopPlan.ts; this file is editable without code changes.",
